    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has clearly been well-loved over the years. Whether you\u2019re commuting or heading out on a weekend road trip, this car is ready to go and super dependable. I\u2019ve taken great care of it, and I\u2019m sure you\u2019ll feel that the moment you get behind the wheel. Come take it for a spin\u2014you won\u2019t be disappointed!",
      "price": 32500.0,
